                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290716-152-off841 t18290716-152-crimeloc843"></join>. On the 20th of June I saw the prisoner standing at his door for about half a minute - then called a person in the street, of the name of Goff; he then jumped up, and took down this shawl - he ran up the market, and round the end of it; I jumped over the counter, and pursued him - I did not lose sight of him for two seconds all the time; I can swear he is the man- the shawl is my master's.</p>
